            p
               | A fully armored stickleback from the ocean near Loberg Lake (top), and a low-armored 
               | stickleback taken from Loberg Lake in 1994 (bottom). The fish have been stained with a dye called Alizarin Red S, which stains bones, in order to 
               | highlight their differences. 
